24
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:54,998
Can you understand that?

25
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:57,435
- I want to come home.
- No...

26
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,989
I miss my children.

27
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:04,153
Be strong my chlld,
you can do lt.

28
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:11,158
Try to be strong.
I know you can do lt.

29
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,434
I'm done now.

30
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:22,470
- Are you finished?
- Yes.

31
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:27,111
- Is the sack empty?
- Yes.

32
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:31,319
Let me see.
You're a really good boy.

33
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:36,349
Wait, I'll go inside.
I have a reward for you.

34
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:47,634
Here you are...
Some candy and mango juice.

35
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:51,190
- That's your favourite, isn't it?
- Yes, thank you.

36
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:56,070
You're a really nice boy,
a hard working boy.

37
00:02:58,080 --> 00:03:00,196
You like that, don't you?

38
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:12,950
I just wanted to ask how...

39
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,918
What?

40
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:22,792
- How much will you pay me?
- Pay you?

41
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:27,351
- I'm not giving you any money.
- But you must pay me.

42
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:31,513
- I did all of this.
- Did you help me for money?

43
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:35,992
Get out of here. Shame on you!
Are you trying to trick me?

44
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:42,315
Go on, leave! Shame on you!
I'm not that easily fooled!

45
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:31,030
- And no sex?
- No.

46
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:35,670
- Nothing?
- No.

47
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:38,195
- Where is he from?
- America.

48
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:40,351
I love Americans.

49
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:43,398
I hate them,
but this one was different.

50
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:48,111
