52
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:54,839
The Italians are worse.

53
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:58,913
Yes, they think they're so good,
they shouldn't have to pay.

54
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:05,189
- But the Germans are the worst.
- The Germans? They're OK.

55
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:08,989
They're dirty.

56
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:11,469
No, not all of them.

57
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:18,034
But the Arabs...
The Arabs are the worst of all.

58
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:23,638
- I wouldn't go with them.
- Nobody would. They stink.

59
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:28,715
How about the Japanese?
I wouldn't go with them.

60
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:32,190
