63
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:46,710
I'm going to look for him tomorrow.
I know where he lives.

64
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:45,550
Time to get up!
We're going somewhere today.

65
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:49,679
Hurry up and get dressed.
Wake up!

66
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:53,515
- But I have school today.
- You're not going to school.

67
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:57,196
I'll be your teacher today.

68
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:06,837
This is yours...
...and this is yours.

69
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:13,278
Tell your brother's teacher
he's home sick today.

70
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:20,637
So you've worked
for that old miserly cheat!

71
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:23,598
