72
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:28,754
- I take good care of you, don't I?
- Yes, grandmother.

73
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:34,836
So why do you keep calling
your mother to complain?

74
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:47,669
Do you know where we're going?

75
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,711
Let's go.

76
00:17:22,120 --> 00:17:24,270
Look at them.

77
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:30,232
This is what they do every day.

78
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:40,954
Look at those kids.
Is this the kind of life you want?

79
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:50,796
Look, he's only your age
and he's already collecting garbage.

80
