Why not?
You haven't eaten anything today.

82
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:21,154
Go on, eat it!

83
00:18:21,320 --> 00:18:25,108
Do you know why your mother
is working in America?

84
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:28,955
So you won't have to eat this bread.

85
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:32,749
So that you can have a good life.

86
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:37,835
A good life, proper food, nice house.

87
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:41,072
A good education.

88
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:44,949
Money, so when you get sick
you can go to the doctor.

89
00:18:45,120 --> 00:18:48,829
Those kids can't go to the doctor.

90
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:56,998
When they get sick, they just die.

91
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,594
They just die.

92
00:19:12,040 --> 00:19:14,349
Are you enjoying your ice cream?

93
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:24,036
