97
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:47,149
- Sell themselves?
- They sell themselves to tourists.

98
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:50,756
They buy kids and take
them to their hotels.

99
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:54,708
Why are they taking the kids
to their hotels?

100
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:59,112
I don't know, they just want
someone to sleep with.

101
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:03,118
