103
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:13,828
Let's not talk about it.
They just sleep, nothing else.

104
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:19,074
They don't do anything,
they just sleep there.

105
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:21,549
Just eat your ice cream.

106
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:33,675
Hey, that's my bike.
What are you doing with it?

107
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:39,949
- It's mine now.
- It's not yours, it's ours.

108
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:42,793
Your slippers... take them off.

109
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:46,430
- Take off your clothes.
- Do you have any money?

110
00:36:47,680 --> 00:36:50,990
You're new around here,
don't be a show off!

111
00:36:56,840 --> 00:37:00,469
Hey, go away!

112
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:07,149
Wake up!

113
