This one's a copy.

137
00:49:24,120 --> 00:49:29,240
Okay, I'll give you 30.
That's my last offer. Agreed?

138
00:51:41,200 --> 00:51:44,237
I'm here now, my son.

139
00:51:45,720 --> 00:51:48,632
I will never leave you again.

140
00:52:06,160 --> 00:52:09,994
Never ever.

141
00:52:11,480 --> 00:52:16,031
How are you, my sweet one?
Are you not asleep yet?

142
00:52:18,320 --> 00:52:23,952
